  <description><![CDATA[<p>Recently renovated the Sogno del Benaco is set within its own gardens just 200m from the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c}" title="Limone">Limone</a>. The new modern design gives the hotel a vibrant feel. The large rooftop terrace is perfect for sunbathing as well as taking in the stunning views over the lake and Limone. There is direct access to the beach and the refurbished 'Jimmy's' beach bar. Guests staying at the Sogno also have access to the facilities at their sister hotel, Garda Bellevue, next door.</p>]]></description>
